divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: I saw the UFO at around 9:35 PM EST on March 19. The UFO was oval-shaped with 4 lights. 2 of them were white and the other 2 changed from blue to green as it flew over me. It seemed to be moving very fast and it made a "looooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooo" sound.
